<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>암기력 훈련 v5.3 - Blind Mode</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Pretendard', -apple-system, sans-serif; background: #f0f2f5; display: flex; justify-content: center; padding: 20px; }
        #app { background: white; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; padding: 30px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); text-align: center; position: relative; }
        .hidden { display: none !important; }
        .vol-fixed { background: #e9ecef; padding: 10px; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: left; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .panel { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; }
        #countdown { font-size: 8rem; color: #228be6; font-weight: bold; margin: 30px 0; }
        button { width: 100%; padding: 18px; font-size: 1.1rem; border: none; border-radius: 10px; cursor: pointer; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.2s; background: #228be6; color: white; }
        button:hover { background: #1c7ed6; }
        
        .btn-mic { background: #f03e3e; margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; min-height: 110px; }
        .btn-mic.recording { background: #ff922b; animation: pulse 1.5s infinite; }
        .stt-visualizer { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 8px; color: #fff; font-weight: bold; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2); padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 15px; }
        
        @keyframes pulse { 0% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.7; } 100% { opacity: 1; } }
        
        .btn-next { background: #40c057; margin-top: 10px; }
        .btn-cancel { background: #868e96; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; padding: 12px; }
        
        /* 보안 입력창: 글자가 절대 보이지 않도록 수정 */
        #u-input { width: 100%; height: 60px; margin-top: 10px; box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 1rem; padding: 15px; border: 2px solid #eee; border-radius: 10px; resize: none; background: #f8f9fa; color: transparent; text-shadow: 0 0 0 #f8f9fa; caret-color: transparent; pointer-events: none; }
        
        .round-badge { background: #e7f5ff; color: #1971c2; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 15px; font-weight: bold; }
        .score-summary { background: #e7f5ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #1971c2; }
        .history-section { margin-top: 30px; text-align: left; border-top: 2px solid #eee; padding-top: 20px; }
        .history-list { max-height: 180px; overflow-y: auto; font-size: 0.85rem; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: 10px;}
        .history-item { padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="app">
    <div class="vol-fixed">
        <label>📢 음량 조절</label>
        <input type="range" id="vol" min="0" max="1" step="0.1" value="0.7" style="width:100%" oninput="updateVol(this.value)">
    </div>

    <div id="round-badge" class="round-badge">맞춤형 암기 훈련</div>
    <h2 id="main-title" style="margin-top:0;">🧠 블라인드 회상 테스트</h2>

    <div id="screens">
        <div id="step-setup">
            <div class="panel">
                <div class="option-item"><label>🎯 훈련 단어 수</label>
                    <select id="wCount" style="width:100%">
                        <option value="5">입문 (5개)</option>
                        <option value="12">보통 (12개)</option>
                        <option value="15">집중 (15개)</option>
                        <option value="24" selected>도전 (24개)</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="option-item" style="margin-top:10px;"><label>⏳ 장기 기억 대기</label>
                    <select id="dTime" style="width:100%; margin-top:5px;">
                        <option value="5">5초(테스트)</option>
                        <option value="600">10분</option>
                        <option value="1200" selected>20분</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button onclick="pressStart()">훈련 시작</button>
            <div class="history-section">
                <div style="font-weight:bold;">📜 최근 기록</div>
                <div id="main-history-list" class="history-list"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="step-ready" class="hidden"><div id="countdown">3</div></div>

        <div id="step-speak" class="hidden">
            <div id="speak-idx" style="font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:bold; color:#e03131;">1 / 15</div>
            <div style="font-size: 5rem; margin: 20px;">📢</div>
            <p>단어를 잘 듣고 암기하세요.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="step-input" class="hidden">
            <div id="input-title" class="round-badge" style="background:#ffec99; color:#f08c00;">회상 단계</div>
            <p id="input-msg" style="margin-bottom:15px; font-weight:bold;">기억나는 단어를 말씀하세요.</p>
            
            <button id="mic-btn" class="btn-mic" onclick="toggleMic()">
                <span id="mic-icon" style="font-size:2rem;">🎤</span>
                <span id="mic-text">음성 인식 시작</span>
                <div id="stt-visualizer" class="stt-visualizer hidden">대기 중...</div>
            </button>

            <textarea id="u-input" readonly placeholder="보안 모드: 음성 인식 시 단어가 보이지 않습니다."></textarea>
            
            <button class="btn-next" onclick="pressNext()">확인 (다음)</button>
        </div>

        <div id="step-wait" class="hidden">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px; color: #495057;">☕ 정보가 장기 기억으로 고정되는 중...</div>
            <div id="wait-timer" style="font-size: 4rem; font-weight: bold; color: #228be6;">00:00</div>
            <button class="btn-cancel" onclick="skipWait()">바로 결과 보기</button>
        </div>

        <div id="step-result" class="hidden">
            <h2 id="final-res">📊 최종 결과</h2>
            <div id="round-scores" class="score-summary"></div>
            <div id="answer-list" style="text-align: left; background:#f8f9fa; padding:15px; border-radius:10px; margin-bottom:20px; line-height:2.2;"></div>
            <button onclick="location.reload()">처음으로</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

